Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He fits snugly in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Wh-Wh-What do you think you're doing?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:32.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I can carry him in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if he's shorter than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:37.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like Otani.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:48.54,title,,0080,0000,0085,,{\fad(1800,0)\3c&H0A0909&\q2\pos(380,395)}A Maiden's Determination! Love-Love Confession Plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:53.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:56.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you? Feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:08.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have come to the seaside for Umibouzu live concert, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I even brought my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and be night time already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to the beach during summer vacation should be about love and youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Love! Romance! Not Umibouzu, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're still trying to hide it at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just admit it to me and I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You llike Otani-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You like him, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:46.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boys and girls, please listen up for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:03:00.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try to give Risa and Otani-kun some alone time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Risa realizing her one-sided love, we all need to do what we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What the heck are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're finally going to confess to Otani-kun, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:15.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, everyone already knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who hasn't realized it is Otani himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.29,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you for ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:42.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.82,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Everyone is so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:42.07,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Nothing at all, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? My turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! This is nothing like the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:05.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi... look, a hermit crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, it hid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.90,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:22.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Suzuki-kun, let's have a race from the beach to the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They're watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:37.71,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all watching my every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:41.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's got you so stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are casual, completely oblivious to other people's problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I have no idea what you're on about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! That's payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch our stuff. You guys go and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Risa will get bored all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun, could you stay with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha... That's... I'll be fine by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're hurt. We can't just leave you on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My main objective for the day is to catch some rays anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well in that case, stay with Risa and you guys can both get a tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! I'll be fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if you tan that skinny body of yours, you won't look any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're got this much time to spare, why don't you go swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:11.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it's like that, huh? Let's go, Nakao, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When I become a lawyer, I'm gonna sue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to swim with Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.54,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too... with Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:27.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked you to get him to sue you?! I told you to confess to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya wanna have some fun together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You really thought someone was trying to pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Resting, resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that was for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drink'em both. Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why didn't you put it over there, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's fault is that? You're the one who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just returning the favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for treating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just being quiet or are you feeling weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I've been wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get you some pain killers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You only just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I happened to accidentally fall for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such disgusting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything better we can talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,With someone like you, there probably isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get your hopes up about ever finding a boyfriend, amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...What's this?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm just a giant amazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun, what did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! She just suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault. I'm just an amazon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You said a mean thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! She's the one who's always calling me a midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi really is weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl in love will always be emotional!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Novu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone you like, Koizumi? Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're denser than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it would end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:32.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.21,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.30,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:36.68,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.55,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.26,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I said {\i1}Hey{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me! What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go get snow cones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:47.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Stop ignoring me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your foot okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to an Umibouzu concert, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about the pain ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what was all that about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The summer sun was just too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So who's this guy you like Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:22.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:26.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Everyone else knows. You're gonna leave me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy you like is shorter than you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you cried when I called you an amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you let stuff like that worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You have your own charm, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be indecisive. Just go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I mind, being the only one who doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is just the type of guy he is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is the type of girl I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean {\i1}"soon enough"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I really do care, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.61,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know if it'll go smoothly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I like him and I just can't help it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The concert is about to start. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment for making me cry, take a picture with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be indecisive. Just go for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You just wait, Otani!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never thought he'd be this slow on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been asking me {\i1}"Who does Koizumi like?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over since we got back from the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, don't forget that Otani-kun is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer vacation is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:12.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Once summer is over, we've got the school trip and a ton of events coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:16.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep procrastinating, you'll have to deal with a ton of rivals going after Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! No, no no! I can't deal with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. I'll help you, but you need to do your best too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely useless using a subtle approach with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to do it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never work if you can't even say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I just have to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you need to get him alone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone? Just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it'd be your first time alone with Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Up till now, we've jsut been together as All Hanshin-Kyojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we get a romantic mood going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible or not, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with being All-Kyojin forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:34.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Let me write this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Gyah"{\i0}? What am I, a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's nothing! We weren't doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about so secretively?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna say {\i1}"right"{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go no. Do it now, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're excluding me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I just have to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Disgusting"{\i0}?! I was trying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've got to say to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone keeps talking about it behind my back. It's really getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one who doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's completely useless using a subtle approach with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're the one I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I possibly say that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.38,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.13,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear what I just said, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.53,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:02.58,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.02,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:04.95,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't say that! That's beyond embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have to do it over summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't tell him now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do it, Risa. Go for it, Risa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just be brave and do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cone on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.64,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTioem-Handwritten\an7\bord0\c&H8C8999&\fs33\pos(334,27)\frz337}I've said a lot of bad things\N\Nup till now, but,\N\Nto be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:21.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:30.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:31.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:49.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just being emotional. You're being downright suspicious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ughh... whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You were shouting during the game too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you, we won today because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't know since you weren't watching at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was watching you the whole time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were so cool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if something is really troubling you, you can always talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to help, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you really consider me that untrustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so distant, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we All Hanshin-Kyojin partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you clutching at your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Can't I clutch at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really like him that much? This guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:44.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:46.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an idiot... but he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:56.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's shorter than me, but he's so sweet that I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the reason you've been coming to watch basketball...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because this guy you like is on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that freshman, Yamamoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If it;s someone shorter than you, and he's on the basketball team, it has to be Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikeda is pretty short too....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:24.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:28.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's that dense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Otani is seriously slow, and hopeless to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. It's not like it matters, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:46.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:53.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right! It's my birthday! I totally forgot for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are perky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already opening it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A fountain you can put on your bathroom wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome! I'm super happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for tonight's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.82,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wanted one for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand her taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:21.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's calling to wish you a happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent a message and told him it's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and answer, or he'll hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:36.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Me"{\i0} Who's {\i1}"me"{\i0}? Stoip trying to act cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You lookin' for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Free?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:51.02,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H04010C&\bord0\frz20\pos(246,393)}Free
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:50.90,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Free! Free! Free! Free! Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I guess I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, meet me on the roof of the big building next to the train station at 7pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof? Why there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:01.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and wear what you wore when we went to the festival, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we meeting in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was that about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not nothing big, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look inside, would you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Umibouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It's the premium edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's been signed. It's my most treasured possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought you said you'd never give this away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I'm giving it to a fan like you, I think God will forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:41.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:46.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is the limited edition badge that came with the CD!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As a treat, I'm giving this to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But these are all just extras.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Extras?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's dark enough. It should be about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There are fireworks today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this place last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling a bit better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been all frustrated and weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought watching the fireworks would cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's appropriate when watching fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}" fine feathers don't make fine birds"{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. They sure are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,really do like Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:18.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's now, I think I can say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:25.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to the guy I like, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:32.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:37.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: Sunk! The Worst Confession in History!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch!
